<lb n="0870c15"/>祇多　羅剃阿羅他僧祇帝　阿彌多婆<note n="0870021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【明】</note><app n="0870021"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>
